      <title>通胀持续，日本提议创纪录上调最低工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/japan-proposes-record-minimum-pay-hike-as-inflation-remains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本劳动省提议连续第四年创纪录地提高最低工资标准，以在物价上涨的情况下为低收入家庭提供支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/japan-proposes-record-minimum-pay-hike-as-inflation-remains</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:36:42 GMT</pubDate>
