    <item>
      <title>巴西因马杜罗言论取消对委内瑞拉选举的访问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/brazil-cancels-electoral-mission-to-venezuela-on-maduro-comment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鉴于尼古拉斯·马杜罗对南美大国委内瑞拉的选举制度发表批评言论，巴西将不会按原计划派专家观察周日举行的委内瑞拉总统选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/brazil-cancels-electoral-mission-to-venezuela-on-maduro-comment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>律师称黎智英将在香港国安​​案审判中作证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/hong-kong-court-rejects-jimmy-lai-s-bid-to-drop-security-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港民主派大亨黎智英将出庭为自己辩护，此案与一起重大国家安全案件有关。此前，法庭驳回了黎智英提出的撤销指控的请求，这位 76 岁老人可能因此被判终身监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/hong-kong-court-rejects-jimmy-lai-s-bid-to-drop-security-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:47:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南为强势党魁举行两天哀悼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/vietnam-begins-two-days-of-mourning-for-powerful-party-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南为越南共产党中央总书记阮富仲举行了为期两天的国葬，阮富仲于上周五去世，标志着该国政治权力结构进入新时代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/vietnam-begins-two-days-of-mourning-for-powerful-party-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本人口下降速度创人口危机以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/japanese-population-falls-at-fastest-pace-in-demographic-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年日本公民数量下降速度为自上世纪 60 年代开始收集数据以来的最快，这给该国的社会保障体系带来了额外压力，并导致劳动力市场萎缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/japanese-population-falls-at-fastest-pace-in-demographic-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:02:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制裁加剧，俄罗斯公司面临越来越多的付款问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/russian-companies-face-mounting-payment-issues-as-sanctions-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京不顾西方国家在国际上孤立他的企图，自 5 月以来与 20 多位世界领导人举行了会晤。俄罗斯企业就没那么幸运了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/russian-companies-face-mounting-payment-issues-as-sanctions-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理阿尔巴尼斯将于周日公布新一届选举前内阁名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/australia-s-pm-albanese-to-reveal-new-pre-election-cabinet-sunday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两名资深部长退休后，澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯 (Anthony Albanese) 将在内阁会议上宣布新内阁名单，这使得中左翼政府在不到 12 个月的选举前做好了准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/australia-s-pm-albanese-to-reveal-new-pre-election-cabinet-sunday</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:35:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国推迟对越南市场经济地位作出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-delays-decision-on-vietnam-s-market-economy-status-by-a-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府宣布是否将越南列为市场经济的决定的时间已延长一周，将于 8 月 2 日之前公布，此举可能促进越南的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-delays-decision-on-vietnam-s-market-economy-status-by-a-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:14:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡在国会演讲中为加沙战争进行激烈辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/netanyahu-tells-congress-us-and-israel-must-stand-together</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡在国会发表演讲，为该国与哈马斯的战争进行激烈辩护，将自己置身于美国政坛的紧张时刻，并嘲笑国会外数千名抗议其对加沙冲突处理方式的示威者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/netanyahu-tells-congress-us-and-israel-must-stand-together</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 18:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选“极难预测” 政策前景蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/-sensationally-unpredictable-us-election-clouds-policy-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国大选前不到四个月，民主党总统候选人的意外更换，给2025年及以后的经济政策前景带来了新的不确定因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/-sensationally-unpredictable-us-election-clouds-policy-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
